Flora is made with sunflower seed oil which contains Omega 6 and vitamin E. Come and visit our website floraspread.com.au or floraspread.co.nz.
A rich, delicious margarine blend with buttermilk, for a big buttery taste with the spreadability of margarine. It's completely delicious and can be used for spreading, cooking and baking.

Flora margarine is made with sunflower seed oil which contains Omega 6 and Vitamin E.

Enjoy Flora Buttery Margarine on toast, dollop it on hot vegetables or melt it over potatoes for the little extra indulgence of buttery taste, but with 65% less saturated fat than butter.

No artificial colours or flavours.

Treat yourself to the irresistible, buttery taste of Flora margarine with 65% less saturated fat than butter.
